These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different games are played: whist, poker, chess, scrabble
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, coach, freelancer, security-guard
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, august, october, november
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, dubstep, rock
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit
City: liverpool, rome, marseilles, berlin
 1. the owner of the rabbit is the fan of dubstep##1
 2. the analyst is the person traveling to rome##1
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 6. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the freelancer is the person playing scrabble##1
10. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
12. the security-guard is the person playing poker##1
13. the analyst is in an even position##4
14. the security-guard is the fan of d&b##1
15. the person who's birthday is in may is the person playing poker##1
16. the analyst is on the left of the person playing chess##1
17. the coach is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |       4        |
| Game         | scrabble    | whist      | chess | poker        |
| Job           | freelancer | analyst     | coach     | security-guard |
| Birthday   | august   | october | november   | may         |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | rock        | dubstep   | d&b            |
| Pet           | bird       | chinchilla  | rabbit    | lizard         |
| City     | liverpool       | rome     | berlin     | marseilles      |

