 4. the person playing bridge is the person traveling to nizza##1
 5. the person playing bridge is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the person traveling to paris is the person playing canasta##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the modern house##1
 8. the modern house is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
 9. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the train##1
10. the person playing canasta is the person watching spy movies##1
11. the palace house is in an odd position##4
12. the person watching action movies is the person driving the train##1
13. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
14. the owner of the mouse is the person watching spy movies##1
15. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the craftsman house##1
16. the person playing domino is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
17. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
18. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
