 3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
 4. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1
 5. the german is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 6. the librarian is the person who likes lavender##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the lizard and the pakistani##2
