 9. the fan of blues is between the person who likes apricot and the freelancer##2
10. the fan of trance is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
11. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1
12. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
13. the owner of the lizard is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing domino##1

